               <p>Taken before me, J. ANDERSON, April 22, 1822.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220417-149-person1443">
                  WILLIAM 
                  SIMMS
               <interp inst="t18220417-149-person1443" type="surname" value="SIMMS"></interp>
