                     <interp inst="t18220417-149-person1444" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             lodges with me. I was not at home when the lamb was found. The room it was found in belonged to Weedon.</p>
               <p>Two witnesses gave Alsey a good character.</p>
